data.description: Welcome to Blue Haven Cottage!  Located in a desirable section of Del Haven on a quiet dead end residential street with mature trees sits a turnkey home completely renovated (inside) and manicured on the outside.  The exterior has been painted in a soft blue color (Harbor Blue) and boasts all NEW vinyl  replacement windows. The living room, hallway and the two bedrooms have refinished hardwood floors. The kitchen features fashionable quartz countertops and vinyl plank flooring. The tiled bath is a tub/shower combination with a quartz vanity. The heating and air conditioning are fueled by a new mini split HVAC unit.  A new electric hot water heater has been installed in addition to a new exterior electric meter.  The property is connected to city water and city sewer.  The property currently has eight short term rentals secured for the spring and summer months through VRBO and AIRBNB. This is an ideal property for someone who is looking for summer/year round use and the ability to draw rental income.  The furnishings and appliances are brand new and included in the price of the sale.
